   "kind": "global",
   "file": "island.zil",
   "line": 2265,
   "value": "<TABLE 0 \"Your face convulses in a prodigious yawn.\" \"You stare into space for a long, thoughtless moment. It seems\nvery hard to think, you think, but you aren't sure.\" \"Your eyes are extraordinarily dry. You blink to moisten them,\nand snort awake a minute later, drool dripping down your chin.\" \"Sleep overtakes you and you slump into unconsiousness.\">"
